cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the mathematical analysis of the Batch normalization effect on gradient backpropagation in residual network training. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on the analysis of deep learning models, the first three sub-categories are more likely than the last two.
